FAQs.question: What is the return policy?
FAQs.answer: You can return items within 30 days of purchase.

FAQs.question: How do I contact customer service?
FAQs.answer: Customer service can be contacted via phone, email, or chat.

FAQs.question: Can I change my shipping address?
FAQs.answer: Yes, you can change it before the order is shipped.

FAQs.question: How do I use my reward points?
FAQs.answer: Reward points can be applied at checkout.

FAQs.question: How do I cancel my subscription?
FAQs.answer: Subscriptions can be canceled in the 'Subscription' section.

FAQs.question: Why is my payment declined?
FAQs.answer: Ensure your payment details are correct and funds are sufficient.

FAQs.question: What are the delivery options?
FAQs.answer: Standard and express delivery options are available.

FAQs.question: Can I update my email address?
FAQs.answer: Yes, you can update it in the 'Account Settings' section.

FAQs.question: What should I do if I receive a damaged item?
FAQs.answer: Contact support immediately to report the issue.

FAQs.question: How can I track my support ticket?
FAQs.answer: You can track your support tickets in the 'Support' section.
